297
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,120
I told you about it.

298
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,320
When?

299
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:58,160
Just give me a second, okay?

300
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:03,280
