-Okay.

304
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,560
Umang, just start the costume trial.

305
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:13,120
I'll quickly wrap up the interview.

306
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,360
Need any help?

307
