accepted for who I am...

322
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:18,280
is the greatest gift
that my fans could give me.

323
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:20,200
-Ma'am...
-I'm so grateful.

324
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:22,480
Samara ma'am has chosen
