335
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,200
No, I guess.

336
00:16:58,440 --> 00:16:59,720
Let's fix that.

337
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,000
Drink?

338
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:04,880
Oh, my God. Baby, I'm so sorry
