00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:54,280
C'mon! C'mon!

442
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:56,040
-C'mon!
-Tag!

443
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,840
-C'mon!
-Tag.

444
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,000
Sushmita, tag anybody.

445
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:01,920
-Sushmita!
-Sushmita, tag.

