00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,680
Please stop.

450
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:15,600
No, no, no!

451
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,800
Fuck!

452
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,800
-Anj, are you okay?
