489
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,040
Come with us.
Come.

490
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:42,200
Okay.

491
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,320
Mom, mom!
Wait. Listen.

492
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:47,920
